<Base title="Privacy Policy | INNO Transformer Temperature" description="Read the privacy policy for the static INNO transformer temperature website and direct email communications."><section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>This static website does not contain a contact form or create a customer account.</p></div></section><section class="section"><article class="container prose"><h2>Website interaction</h2><p>The site presents public product and technical information. It does not ask visitors to enter inquiry information into a web form.</p><h2>Email communication</h2><p>If you choose to email INNO, your email provider sends the message and attachments. Information you provide can be used to understand and respond to your product or project inquiry.</p><h2>Technical hosting data</h2><p>Hosting and security providers can process routine request information such as IP address, browser, requested URL and time for delivery, reliability and abuse prevention. Their handling follows their applicable policies.</p><h2>Contact</h2><p>Privacy questions about this website can be sent to <a href="mailto:fjinnonet@gmail.com">fjinnonet@gmail.com</a>.</p></article></section></Base>
